title: Mike Pence Joins the Progrum
description: The fellas welcome a big guest, former Vice President Mike Pence, to the progrum. They also banter about Dem disarray, animal fighting and politician Matthew Dowd before welcoming Hollywood Henn to discuss the latest #FreeBritney drama. Oh they also play King of the Hill.
